metadata.name: Mutant Dreams
metadata.description:
"Eldritch's Fashion Fear - Body Couture" is a unique drop that fuses cosmic horror, fashion, and cyberwire elements.

The Drop features 40 striking artworks that showcase otherworldly styles and grotesque mutations, drawing the viewer in with their surreal sensual beauty. With attention to detail, color, and texture, this Drop is a must-see for those who enjoy pushing the boundaries of horror and fashion.

All Artworks are in 4000*4000 Pixel
